            <div class="warning-box">
                <h3>The Theta Problem</h3>
                <p><strong>Observation:</strong> Almost half of WeWork's innovation effort went into Edge, and a significant portion into Beyond. Core, which should sustain revenue, was smaller and weaker than it needed to be.</p>
